# Boom Tech x NDR Character Specification

When generating images that include the Boom Tech mascot character via Nano Banana MCP, always follow this canonical character description. The character must remain visually consistent across all generated images.

## Character Design

### Physical Appearance
- Female character — do NOT generate as male
- Bright spiky red hair swept dramatically upward and backward
- Red headband across the forehead
- Sharp, determined anime-style eyes with feminine features
- Slender, athletic build matching the original Boom Tech poster art
- Confident or focused expression (smirk for casual, intense for action)

### Goggles
- Steampunk-style goggles with deep navy blue (#1F2147) frames
- Always pushed up on the forehead, never covering the eyes
- Circular lenses with subtle glare detail

### Outfit
- **Labcoat**: flowing white labcoat, open in front, with red (#A31921) accent trim along collar, cuffs, and lapel edges; labcoat billows or flows in action poses
- **Tie**: bold red (#A31921) necktie, clearly visible between the labcoat lapels
- **Undershirt**: dark/black shirt beneath the labcoat and tie
- **Pants**: black fitted pants
- **Boots**: dark navy (#1F2147) combat boots with red (#A31921) laces
- **Gloves**: dark fingerless gloves (optional, action poses only)

### Employee Badge (Required)
- Single lanyard-style employee ID badge worn around the neck
- The badge displays ONLY the NDR shield logo (no wordmark, no "National Debt Relief" text)
- The shield is the registered trademark shield: navy blue (#1F2147) shield shape with red (#A31921) flag/banner accent and small decorative stars
- White rectangular badge card with a metal clip attached to a navy blue lanyard
- Only ONE badge; never duplicate badges on the coat or arms

### Weapon (Variant-Dependent)
- **Action variant**: large dark metallic rocket launcher / bazooka carried over one shoulder; navy blue body with red accent highlights and red tip
- **Casual variant**: no weapon at all; hands free for confident gestures (adjusting goggles, hand on hip, arms crossed, pointing)

## NDR Brand Colors (Always Use)
- Deep Navy Blue: #1F2147
- Flag Red: #A31921
- White background for all images unless specified otherwise
- Light Blue (#D1E9FF) for supporting card/node backgrounds in diagrams

